def calculate_min_rotations(R: str, D: str) -> int:
    c = 1
    n = len(R)
    for i in range(n):
        R_digit = int(R[i])
        D_digit = int(D[i])
        c1 = abs(R_digit - D_digit)
        c2 = abs(R_digit - (D_digit + 10))
        c3 = abs(R_digit + 10 - D_digit)
        c += min(c1, c2, c3)
    return c
